                <div class="card">
                    <h3>Pilih Area Pembersihan</h3>
                    <p style="color:var(--text-muted); margin-bottom:20px;">Pilih jenis file sampah yang ingin Anda hapus.</p>
                    
                    <div class="clean-options">
                        <label class="clean-option-card selected">
                            <input type="checkbox" checked value="registry">
                            <div class="clean-option-icon">📝</div>
                            <div style="font-weight:600;">Registry</div>
                            <div style="font-size:12px; color:var(--text-muted); margin-top:5px;">Entri tidak valid</div>
                        </label>
                        <label class="clean-option-card selected">
